title: Assistant says "will be ready soon" but doesn't work. Voice match is activated. Pixel 5 phone.
content: I set up voice match but when I swipe or say "hey Google" or "hello Google" nothing happens. It just says "assistant will be ready soon" - I got this phone 48 hours ago. Surely it should be set up by now?
category: Google Assistant and Voice Actions, Google Pixel 5
